I don't know if you made these videos but if you did Thank you so much. I pray that if there is a DVD/broadcast of the tour that its not edited anything like the MDNA/RHT because its a shame because I can't watch them. RHT one actually makes me feel sick with motion sickness and I get a headache! I wish she would hire some of him really talented fans because they as demonstrated here they can provide an edit that a fan wants. Edited from a fan's desire.
I miss the golden days when HBO would broadcast the tours. The video/DVD was then a slightly differently edited version. Anyway much love...thank you again. ‚ù§‚ù§üéâüéâ
